  "Rosters": {
    "Description": "Table: Rosters",
    "important": true,
    "summary_rich": "The **teams**. Each roster belongs to an owner and accumulates its players' stats through `RosterAssignments`. A roster's `ProjectedScore` is a **second-order calc** — it sums the assigned players' raw yardage and TDs, then applies the scoring formula again at the team level. Add or drop a player and the roster total moves in real time.",
    "important_fields": ["Name", "Owner", "TotalTouchdowns", "ProjectedScore"],
    "schema": [
      {
        "name": "RosterId",
        "datatype": "string",
        "type": "raw",
        "nullable": false,
        "Description": "Team slug (PK)"
      },
      {
        "name": "Name",
        "datatype": "string",
        "type": "calculated",
        "nullable": false,
        "Description": "Display name",
        "formula": "={{RosterId}}"
      },
      {
        "name": "Owner",
        "datatype": "string",
        "type": "raw",
        "nullable": false,
        "Description": "Owner email"
      },
      {
        "name": "TotalPassingYards",
        "datatype": "integer",
        "type": "aggregation",
        "nullable": false,
        "Description": "Sum of QB passing yards on roster",
        "formula": "=SUMIFS(RosterAssignments!{{PassingYards}}, RosterAssignments!{{Roster}}, {{RosterId}})"
      },
      {
        "name": "TotalRushingYards",
        "datatype": "integer",
        "type": "aggregation",
        "nullable": false,
        "Description": "Sum of rushing yards on roster",
        "formula": "=SUMIFS(RosterAssignments!{{RushingYards}}, RosterAssignments!{{Roster}}, {{RosterId}})"
      },
      {
        "name": "TotalReceivingYards",
        "datatype": "integer",
        "type": "aggregation",
        "nullable": false,
        "Description": "Sum of receiving yards on roster",
        "formula": "=SUMIFS(RosterAssignments!{{ReceivedYards}}, RosterAssignments!{{Roster}}, {{RosterId}})"
      },
      {
        "name": "TotalTouchdowns",
        "datatype": "integer",
        "type": "aggregation",
        "nullable": false,
        "Description": "Sum of all TDs on roster",
        "formula": "=SUMIFS(RosterAssignments!{{TotalTouchdowns}}, RosterAssignments!{{Roster}}, {{RosterId}})"
      },
      {
        "name": "TotalInterceptions",
        "datatype": "integer",
        "type": "aggregation",
        "nullable": false,
        "Description": "Sum of INTs on roster",
        "formula": "=SUMIFS(RosterAssignments!{{Interceptions}}, RosterAssignments!{{Roster}}, {{RosterId}})"
      },
      {
        "name": "ProjectedScore",
        "datatype": "number",
        "type": "calculated",
        "nullable": false,
        "Description": "Total roster fantasy points (2nd-order calc)",
        "formula": "=ROUND(({{TotalPassingYards}} / 25) + ({{TotalRushingYards}} / 10) + ({{TotalReceivingYards}} / 10) + ({{TotalTouchdowns}} * 6) - ({{TotalInterceptions}} * 2), 2)",
        "important": true,
        "explanation_rich": "**The team-level scoring formula — note the rushing and receiving lines.** Rosters use a slightly different weighting than individual players: 1 point per 25 passing yards, 1 per 10 rushing yards, 1 per 10 receiving yards (PPR-style), 6 per TD, -2 per pick. The same formula runs over the *summed* per-roster totals — that's why it's called a second-order calc: every input is itself an aggregation. Worked example: *Mahomes Mob* (Mahomes + McCaffrey + Kelce) rolls up to 5500 pass yds + 2010 rush yds + 1850 recv yds + 81 TDs + 8 INTs → `(5500/25) + (2010/10) + (1850/10) + (81*6) - (8*2) = 220 + 201 + 185 + 486 - 16 = 1076.00`. Trade Kelce for a backup TE and the number drops the same instant."
      }
    ],
